data.description: Check out this beautiful home. Newer custom made hickory cabinets in the kitchen and a newer half bath in the lower level are some of the improvements inside. Heated and cooled garage, storage shed with electricity,  invisible fence, irrigation system and new deck are part of the outside upgrades. 3 bedrooms on one level is a bonus. Close to everything. Only a block away from the city swimming pool, ice rink, fairgrounds, Hannahs Bend park and even fishing and the bike trail are all within minutes and no busy roads to cross to get to them.
